{"tid":2432532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《立場》揭外判商「交樽仔」採樣日期虛假　採樣日期今起「被消失」","createTime":"2021-03-04T11:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T13:12:22.000Z","uid":261647,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9f170edc56e875064949e2f49fcd9dabcd3e6ad3","tid":2432532,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:42:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/外判商-交樽仔-屢現假採樣日期-政府網站採樣日期今起-被消失/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4%E5%95%86-%E4%BA%A4%E6%A8%BD%E4%BB%94-%E5%B1%A2%E7%8F%BE%E5%81%87%E6%8E%A1%E6%A8%A3%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E6%8E%A1%E6%A8%A3%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F%E4%BB%8A%E8%B5%B7-%E8%A2%AB%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=287eb7d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%A4%96%E5%88%A4%E5%95%86-%E4%BA%A4%E6%A8%BD%E4%BB%94-%E5%B1%A2%E7%8F%BE%E5%81%87%E6%8E%A1%E6%A8%A3%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E6%8E%A1%E6%A8%A3%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F%E4%BB%8A%E8%B5%B7-%E8%A2%AB%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%2F&h=636194dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/外判商-交樽仔-屢現假採樣日期-政府網站採樣日期今起-被消失/</a><br />\n<br />\n醫管局外判商負責的「交樽仔」（深喉唾液樣本）檢測，本周被揭有多宗電子結果出現虛假採樣日期，醫管局至今未正面回應。《立場》接獲多名讀者投訴指，今日（3 日）在政府 EVT 網站查閱「交樽仔」結果時，發現沒有顯示採樣日期。讀者提供的截圖顯示，最早今日（3 日）早上約 10 時半查閱的電子結果，已沒有顯示採樣日期。"},{"pid":"c23335e84dd223919fd783d02a28c79ea9431b02","tid":2432532,"uid":54721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:45:33.000Z","msg":"冇日期就唔會遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ae621ff9b9c1a69ca1a0b98bda10384e706bee","tid":2432532,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:52:22.000Z","msg":"全部陰性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf61f10e062a06d3dfe1bbc51312af1dafe0f9f","tid":24325